TASK 1 - WHAT IS NETWORKING?
• Network = Two or more connected devices that can communicate and share data.
• Examples: Internet, power grid, transport systems, mobile networks.
• Devices on a network can include computers, phones, servers, routers, cameras, and IoT devices.
• Networking is a fundamental concept in Cyber Security because attackers and defenders operate across networks.
KEY TERM
