TASK 2 - WHAT IS THE INTERNET?
• Internet = A global network made up of many smaller networks.
• Invented through the evolution of ARPANET (1960s).
• World Wide Web (WWW) was created by Tim Berners-Lee in 1989.
• Networks are classified as:
•	Private Network (Home, Office)
•	Public Network (Internet)
IMPORTANT CONCEPT
